reviewText: Enjoying very much. Great insights to and from pastors. No defects, product is new.

All I can say is in these last days, what else would you rather be doing with your life?  If you're 18 or 80, and you know that God is calling you to the ministry, be sure to listen to these messages and say, "Here am I, send me!"

If you are not familiar with Calvary Chapel Conferences, then you need to check this one out.  This conference has some of the best speakers in the world teaching on various topics.  This conference focuses on the last days of the Earth, and gives biblical backing for each session taught.  There are seriously so many messages in this pack!  You will be listening, and listening, and watching, and listening.  Buy it!
I attended this conference in Ca. in June. It was incredible and informative. Do yourslef a favor and buy this set of DVDs.
